thread.title: Leigh & Megan
thread.title_full: Nelson Alexander reviewed by Leigh & Megan

author: Leigh & Megan
title: Leigh & Megan
text:
David Mogford delivered everything he promised. From being punctual for all meetings & house openings, to being able to be contacted for queries at all times.
We could not be in attendance for our auction, however David personally kept us up to date with all proceedings. Auction result was above our expectation.
